{% include "shared/vfs-full" %}

## Navigation-Specific Anti-Patterns

| Anti-pattern | Correct approach |
|-|-|
| `Read file.{{ ext }}` then scan for a function | `Read {{ paths.sym_overview("file." ~ ext) }}` → `Read {{ paths.sym("file." ~ ext, "fn_name", ext) }}` |
| `Grep "fn process" src/` to find symbols | `ls {{ paths.by_kind("file." ~ ext, "fn") }}` or read `{{ FILE_OVERVIEW }}` |
| Reading a full file to check imports | `Read {{ paths.imports("file." ~ ext, ext) }}` |
| Reading a file to count symbols | `Read {{ paths.sym_overview("file." ~ ext) }}` (includes counts) |
| Grep + manual line math to find a symbol | `readlink {{ paths.at_line("file." ~ ext, 42) }}` (instant lookup) |

